And you know what ? the guy(s) who wrote the story told that it was the last one he would write, because only people who already played the saga were interested, and it was not giving him enough money. Well, he wrote some 1 or 2 after, but much easier, for noobs.. and he got lot of money.<br />
<br />
..<br />
and, of course, they moved into Ultime Online, but that's totally a different story. Nothing to see with THE AVATAR.
                  
